{"tid":1176046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學生動源」籲全體學生團結反送中：港處危急存亡之秋","createTime":"2019-05-29T03:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T04:30:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb3dc3b77e3a4fb306f27b99ea81edc24b2018f","tid":1176046,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559098804_9f69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559098804_9f69.jpg&h=9277fdd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多間大專院校、中學的組織先後發起聯署反送中惡法，提倡港獨的學生組織「學生動源」亦發出「告全港學生書」，強調逃犯條例修訂草案審議在即，香港現今乃危急存亡之秋，而長久以來學生都是抗爭運動必不可少的力量，呼籲6月9日全體學生一同走上街頭，對抗惡法修訂，「日內學生動源會公佈反逃犯條例修訂入校計劃，屆時將公佈計劃詳情，歡迎全體學生加入有關計劃將反逃犯條例修訂意識帶入校園」。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」指出，近年學生力量在抗爭路上沉寂多時，但現時香港正處於危急存亡之秋，一旦條例修訂通過，勢必嚴重影響香港人生活環境，因此懇請全體中學生、大學生與他們團結一致反修例，保衞我城。<br />\n「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林在其個人facebook指，希望聯絡發起中學組織聯署的人士，以便進行反修例入校計劃。他又表示，其母校佛教茂峰法師紀念中學的舊生，主動找他參與該校的校友師生聯署聲明，令他很感動。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林表示，「學生動源」於6.9大遊行時，會在隊尾竪起組織旗旘作記認，「如非必要學生動源不會採取非常手段以作抗爭，但學生動源絕不會畏懼採取任何抗爭手段！希望全體學生屆時在加入學生動源隊伍！」<br />\n鍾翰林早前於立會外參與反修例活動時，被指搶去1名示威者手持的旗桿上國旗，涉嫌刑事毀壞被捕，其後獲准保釋。"},{"pid":"273e2468530a92fe9b070e96f7ba9b2e69dec78a","tid":1176046,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4d25e634e8a0e3af5fee48103daf6a4491f5d3","tid":1176046,"uid":170135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"我放低左書包好多年喇...<br />\n可唔可以比我加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生終於有行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7634a940a967e79bb45325e0d5acfe182a6312ce","tid":1176046,"uid":211900,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"不了聽日要返學"},{"pid":"fab5142d7873a8cc6aa940e515a074ee1e085005","tid":1176046,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2f3ec39ac6df8454852ec1fc1889f2ce275c36","tid":1176046,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"共党說逃犯唔係針對政治犯？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAY7Uk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAY7Uk2.jpg&h=97fc8884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwYGYNM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwYGYNM.png&h=0e265d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9oLF1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9oLF1n.jpg&h=02ee7e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3YLF1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3YLF1y.jpg&h=54b5776a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gn3Pofu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGn3Pofu.png&h=086e36ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc64b9c3ca9274d06410a4d60a0359081070b0b6","tid":1176046,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"正呀喂，屌你個閪，人群肯定打爆銅鑼灣 天后 跑台山 灣仔"}]}